title: Hmm, I think there's a problem here

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: Sooo, while opening hextech chests. I ended up getting an icon. When I was looking at it I noticed the name of it. I believe there might be a problem XD. Its the Pix icon for Star Guardian Lulu, but it says Little Devil Teemo.

replies.body:
Heyo! 

We've noticed this being an issue with several icons! We're in the process of rolling through all of the icons and ensuring they're all named properly. :)
It's telling us that pix is evil ;)
